Don't trust the test. I had a blood test done to see if I had preeclampsia and it came back negative. 2 weeks later I had to get an emergency cesarean because my preeclampsia was so bad. Go back to the hospital if it gets worse. The only cure for preeclampsia is delivery of your baby
